metadata.name: Wolfpack
metadata.description: The official discord access passes for .JPEG's 10th season. Each NFT grants the owner access to our discord community and serves as a membership pass until the end of the season at which time these passes will be burned in order to claim a new one for next season. Each membership comes with access to our investment community, drop calendar, calls, support, tools, monitors, giveaways and much more. Season 10 officially ends on July 31st, 2022.
